  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About The Game:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tiny Car Mess</strong> throws you straight into a chaotic, pint-sized world of soft-body car mayhem! Get ready to drift, crash, and destroy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/9d6b07b3479f3da8ee914ab3d9bc0e98.poster.avif?t=1771160170\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/9d6b07b3479f3da8ee914ab3d9bc0e98.webm?t=1771160170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/9d6b07b3479f3da8ee914ab3d9bc0e98.mp4?t=1771160170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Epic Derby Action:</strong> Join a derby with up to 24 participants, creating a whirlwind of chaos on the tracks.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/0f1da662e1ba92c6a2b0029fe0cdf211.poster.avif?t=1771160170\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/0f1da662e1ba92c6a2b0029fe0cdf211.webm?t=1771160170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/0f1da662e1ba92c6a2b0029fe0cdf211.mp4?t=1771160170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Two Maps:</strong> Standard concrete arena and a new dirt arena with dirt physics!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2-Player Splitscreen:</strong> Compete with friends or dive into 1v1 showdowns!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/2f5b3207782320224683c2c0ba60ae55.poster.avif?t=1771160170\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/2f5b3207782320224683c2c0ba60ae55.webm?t=1771160170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/2f5b3207782320224683c2c0ba60ae55.mp4?t=1771160170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Power-Ups That Pack a Punch</strong><br>Take chaos to the next level with <strong>all-new power-ups</strong>:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nitro</strong> – For that burst of ridiculous speed.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Revolver</strong> – It's a roulette. Or who knows, you might even get lucky with a whole 6-shooter!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Homing Rocket</strong> – Fire and forget — This rocket chases down its target... Most of the time...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mine</strong> – Watch your rivals fly when they touch it.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/2ec2ed02f8b9d14a68ce748eeda47f9b.poster.avif?t=1771160170\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/2ec2ed02f8b9d14a68ce748eeda47f9b.webm?t=1771160170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/2ec2ed02f8b9d14a68ce748eeda47f9b.mp4?t=1771160170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New Minimap: </strong>Stay on track and find your enemies easily with the brand-new minimap. You’ll always know where the action is.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Control Variety:</strong> Choose your preferred playstyle with support for keyboard, PlayStation controller, and Xbox controller inputs. Feel the drift, master the turns, and outmaneuver your opponents with the control scheme that suits you best. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Remote Play:</strong> Share the joy of chaos with friends far and wide using Steam Remote Play. Invite friends! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to drift, crash, and dominate the derby? Take the wheel!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About The Game:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tiny Car Mess</strong> throws you straight into a chaotic, pint-sized world of soft-body car mayhem! Get ready to drift, crash, and destroy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/9d6b07b3479f3da8ee914ab3d9bc0e98.poster.avif?t=1771160170\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/9d6b07b3479f3da8ee914ab3d9bc0e98.webm?t=1771160170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/9d6b07b3479f3da8ee914ab3d9bc0e98.mp4?t=1771160170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Epic Derby Action:</strong> Join a derby with up to 24 participants, creating a whirlwind of chaos on the tracks.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/0f1da662e1ba92c6a2b0029fe0cdf211.poster.avif?t=1771160170\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/0f1da662e1ba92c6a2b0029fe0cdf211.webm?t=1771160170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/0f1da662e1ba92c6a2b0029fe0cdf211.mp4?t=1771160170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Two Maps:</strong> Standard concrete arena and a new dirt arena with dirt physics!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2-Player Splitscreen:</strong> Compete with friends or dive into 1v1 showdowns!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/2f5b3207782320224683c2c0ba60ae55.poster.avif?t=1771160170\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/2f5b3207782320224683c2c0ba60ae55.webm?t=1771160170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/2f5b3207782320224683c2c0ba60ae55.mp4?t=1771160170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Power-Ups That Pack a Punch</strong><br>Take chaos to the next level with <strong>all-new power-ups</strong>:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nitro</strong> – For that burst of ridiculous speed.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Revolver</strong> – It's a roulette. Or who knows, you might even get lucky with a whole 6-shooter!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Homing Rocket</strong> – Fire and forget — This rocket chases down its target... Most of the time...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mine</strong> – Watch your rivals fly when they touch it.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/2ec2ed02f8b9d14a68ce748eeda47f9b.poster.avif?t=1771160170\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/2ec2ed02f8b9d14a68ce748eeda47f9b.webm?t=1771160170\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2691200/extras/2ec2ed02f8b9d14a68ce748eeda47f9b.mp4?t=1771160170\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New Minimap: </strong>Stay on track and find your enemies easily with the brand-new minimap. You’ll always know where the action is.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Control Variety:</strong> Choose your preferred playstyle with support for keyboard, PlayStation controller, and Xbox controller inputs. Feel the drift, master the turns, and outmaneuver your opponents with the control scheme that suits you best. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Remote Play:</strong> Share the joy of chaos with friends far and wide using Steam Remote Play. Invite friends! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to drift, crash, and dominate the derby? Take the wheel!</p>",
